Specification.name: description
value: Dramatic geometry, scale, and depth, Bogart is a design that wants to live large. Soaring ceilings and a deep sightline really bring this design to its full realization. The bold slanted lines best offset simple vertical and horizontal attributes in the space.

Specification.name: description
value: An alternating grid of concentric rectangles sparks a dynamic interplay with linear architectural elements and the reflective surface pattern. Concentric inevitably creates interesting tangents and provides an engaging visual treat.

Specification.name: description
value: This intense stencil pattern provides strong interplay with light. As shown, a blue luminescent base sits beneath circular mottled textures. It’s a beautiful and unexpected backdrop.

Specification.name: description
value: The digital era has spawned a whole vein of abstract design. Intense colour with mathematical plays of pattern and chaos. A reflective mylar substrate provides additional impact.

Specification.name: description
value: Neutral and dynamic at the same time, this design silhouettes simple geometric profiles very well. Kaleidoscope serves its simple design function with undeniably sophisticated style.

Specification.name: description
value: The undeniable impact of Medallion resounds throughout any space it occupies and provides a strong visual presence.

Specification.name: description
value: Invite spiritual balance in to your spatial design with the beautiful Mandala. Graphically crisp and tailored, this Hindu- inspired design will propel your space into harmonious bliss.

Specification.name: description
value: A textural tour-de-force. Polaris takes simple colour palettes and amplifies impact to 11. This design is incredibly rich, but calm in effect. It also plays very well in more enclosed spaces.

Specification.name: description
value: Radiate a sense of adventure and style. This statement motif turns heads throughout any space it occupies, and works well with strong perpendiculars.

value: Bold, but not brash, this optically-engaging design speaks of mathematical precision and rich visual engagement within the space. Spirograph provides the sense that something exciting is sure to follow.

value: Sumptuous, dramatic and unwilling to take a back seat, this motif is an active participant in the entire spatial design. Visual dynamism in luxury attire is the statement here.

value: A tranquil horizontal ombre with depth, Painted Stucco brings age, earth and a strong linear backdrop to set off your foreground.

Specification.name: description
value: We’ve all heard of this beautiful style of ceiling, but a coffered wall is something to behold. Nesting Squares stylishly demonstrates just how opulent a monochromatic palette can be.

Specification.name: description
value: This highly decorative motif celebrates the artistic air of a Native American culture. Navajo hearkens to a creative spirit and appreciation for the natural world. As this pattern is ornate, a more basic sensibility for the overall space works well.

Specification.name: description
value: Take a universally recognizable motif graphically distilled to its essence, then inject a bold pop feel and you’ve got Mock Croc. This design is so simple and bold, it is a statement that cannot be ignored.

value: Incredibly dramatic yet static in nature, this Orient-inspired design sets off a rich foreground handsomely. All about contrast, this motif simultaneously takes the spotlight and sits back to allow other elements to speak.

Specification.name: description
value: This highly-kinetic surface pattern introduces a bold personality and clean diagonal lines. Kinetic craves attention, a feature location with symmetry in the foreground is a sure fire approach.

Specification.name: description
value: The larger than life floral motif radiates with metallic accents and bold stylized strokes. It’s a timeless design proving that formal need not feel old fashioned.

value: Alternating perpendiculars in contrasting palettes, Don’t Cross the Line provides a space with clean geometry and strong contrasting hues in a rich visual performance.

Specification.name: description
value: No wallflower here, this design takes a botanical element and elevates the presentation to an epic graphic statement. With its overlapping layers and lack of perpendicular lines, this product nicely sets off solid elements and simple lines.

Specification.name: description
value: Rustic yet contemporary, Broken Lattice brings a stylish and airy asymmetrical motif to more intimate spaces.

Specification.name: description
value: A celebration of concrete, the building material of the modern age. This aged look brings raw elegance to contemporary spaces, and the sophisticated chevron repeat sets off straight lines with style.

value: A chic reboot on a primitive ornamental style. Aztec shows a sense of past culture, but with a personal confidence to reinterpret for the present.
